{"tid":1563251,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我哋唔要惠譽評級粒子彈？？？","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T00:09:05.000Z","uid":297897,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f050f8a0454423f43ad14b33f04b9d65c6b5c087","tid":1563251,"uid":297897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"評級機構惠譽下調香港評級，由「AA+」下調至「AA」，展望評級負面。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽指出，持續數月的衝突及暴力事件，正測試一國兩制框架的韌性，雖然預計框架將保持不變，但<span style=\"color: red;\">香港在經濟、金融及社會政治方面，與中國的聯繫逐步提升，反映香港持續融入國家治理體系，將帶來更大的體制及監管挑戰，令到香港與中國的主權評級差距收窄</span>。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽目前對中國的評級為「A+」，展望評級穩定。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽亦指出，即使對示威者要求作出讓步，香港仍存在一定程度的公眾不滿情緒，社會動盪可能再度爆發，或進一步削弱對公營機構的信心、損害對香港管治、制度、政治穩定及營商環境的看法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">評級調低左之後，班高官急著輪着出嚟洗地，經濟不嬲係香港春袋，依粒子彈用得好，會吸引到好多中產同藍絲支持我地，點解過咗咁多日都冇人用，想讓政府半臂？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a45d966fcb1e20a6bf80a510a5328968b9cb86ea","tid":1563251,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bb81ad75d5fa9adbc23bc67b1ea5ef6042fc085","tid":1563251,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f5aacbaa23bd449982b1c